    "Name": "New Dawn",
    "Details": "The ND-RR2 shifts focus to longer range engagement, pairing a Gauss Rifle with a Plasma Rifle as primary weapons. The Plasma Rifle adds heat denial capability alongside direct damage, complicating enemy heat management at range. Twelve tons of armor improves protection over the ND-RR1. Four jump jets are retained. Two ER Medium Lasers provide close-range backup when the primary weapons are reloading or ammunition runs low.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Easy to Maintain</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.09</color></b>",
